source.sqlReaderQuery:
SELECT DISTINCT  
	
	CRM AS CRM_UNIV	          
	,NOME_MEDICO AS MEDICO_UNIV	
	,ESPECIALIDADE	AS ESPECIALIDADE_UNIV
	,ENDERECO	AS LOGRADOURO_UNIV
	,BAIRRO	AS BAIRRO_UNIV
	,CIDADE	AS CIDADE_UNIV
	,CEP	AS CEP_UNIV
	,ORIGEM_END	AS ORIGEM_UNIV
	,UF	AS UF_UNIV
	,BRICK	AS BRICK_UNIV
	,TELEFONE AS TELEFONE_UNIV
FROM 
	"GSK_Intelligence".dbo."DIM_AUDIT_END";

Select distinct
	A.CRM as CRM_GP,
    A.MERCADO as MERCADO_GP,
    A.CATEGORIA as CATEGORIA_GP,
    JORNADA as JORNADA_GP,
    A.CLASSIFICACAO AS QUADRANTE_GP,
    A.ROW_ID_TERRITORIO as ROW_ID_TERRITORIO_GP,
    A.ROW_ID_CONTATO as ROW_ID_CONTATO_GP,
    A.CICLO
From
	"GSK_Intelligence".dbo."Dim_Quadrante_Medico_GP" A
Where 
	LEFT(CAST(A.CICLO AS VARCHAR(10)),4) IN (YEAR(GETDATE()),YEAR(GETDATE())-1) AND
    EXISTS (SELECT B.* FROM "GSK_Intelligence".dbo."DIM_CAD_FORCA_VENDAS" B WHERE A.CICLO = B.CICLO AND A.ROW_ID_TERRITORIO = B.ROW_ID_TERRITORIO 
            AND B.FLAG_BI IS NULL);

SELECT 																						
	A.ACTIVITY_UID AS ID_VISITA,
    A.TARGET_OU_ID AS TIPO_VISITA,
	CASE
	WHEN (A.TARGET_OU_ID = 'F2F') OR
		 (A.TARGET_OU_ID = '') OR
		 (A.TARGET_OU_ID = 'F2F Short call') THEN 'F2F'
	WHEN A.TARGET_OU_ID = 'F2F Accompanied' THEN 'F2F Acompanhada'
	WHEN (A.TARGET_OU_ID = 'Web call') OR 
         (A.TARGET_OU_ID = 'Virtual') THEN 'Virtual'
	WHEN A.TARGET_OU_ID = 'Virtual Accompanied' THEN 'Virtual Acompanhada'      
    WHEN A.TARGET_OU_ID = 'Phone call' THEN 'Telefonica'
    WHEN A.TARGET_OU_ID = 'Sample drop only'THEN 'Entrega Amostras'
    WHEN A.TARGET_OU_ID = 'Item drop only' THEN 'Tentativa de Contato'
	WHEN (A.TARGET_OU_ID = 'Email') OR 
		 (A.TARGET_OU_ID = 'MSL Email') THEN 'Email'
		 ELSE A.TARGET_OU_ID END AS TIPO_VISITA_PTBR,

	CASE
	WHEN A.TARGET_OU_ID = 'F2F' THEN 2
    WHEN A.TARGET_OU_ID = 'F2F Accompanied' THEN 1
    WHEN A.TARGET_OU_ID = 'F2F Short call' THEN 2
	WHEN (A.TARGET_OU_ID = 'Web call') OR 
         (A.TARGET_OU_ID = 'Virtual') THEN 4
	WHEN A.TARGET_OU_ID = 'Phone call' THEN 6
    WHEN A.TARGET_OU_ID = 'Virtual Accompanied' THEN 5
    WHEN A.TARGET_OU_ID = 'Sample drop only' THEN 7
    WHEN A.TARGET_OU_ID = 'Item drop only'THEN 3
	WHEN (A.TARGET_OU_ID = 'Email') OR 
		 (A.TARGET_OU_ID = 'MSL Email') THEN 9
	WHEN A.TARGET_OU_ID = 'MSL On Demand' THEN 8
	ELSE A.TARGET_OU_ID END AS TIPO_VISITA_ORDER,
	A.CLM_IND,
	A.RECORD_TYPE_ID,
	A.RECORD_TYPE_NAME,
	A.DATA,
	A.CICLO,
    A.TARGET_PER_ID,
    A.ROW_ID_TERRITORIO,
	CASE
	 WHEN (DATEPART(weekday,A.DATA) - DATEPART(weekday,DATEADD(month, DATEDIFF(month,0,A.DATA),0)) + 1) < 1 THEN 'S1'
     ELSE	'S' + CAST(((DATEPART(weekday,A.DATA) - DATEPART(weekday,DATEADD(month, DATEDIFF(month,0,A.DATA),0)) + 1)) AS varchar) END AS SEMANA,
    LEFT(FLAG_VISITA,2) as FLAG_VISITA,
	'VR' AS TIPO_INTERACAO
FROM 
	"GSK_Intelligence".dbo."Fato_visitas_Realizadas" A
WHERE 
	LEFT(CAST(A.CICLO AS VARCHAR(10)),4) IN (YEAR(GETDATE()),YEAR(GETDATE())-1) AND
    EXISTS (SELECT B.* FROM "GSK_Intelligence".dbo."DIM_CAD_FORCA_VENDAS" B WHERE A.CICLO = B.CICLO AND A.ROW_ID_TERRITORIO = B.ROW_ID_TERRITORIO 
            AND B.FLAG_BI IS NULL);

Select  
  A.CICLO	
  ,A.ROW_ID_TERRITORIO	
  ,A.ROW_ID_CONTATO	
  ,A.VP	
  ,A.VR	
  ,A.VRE	
  ,A.VRT
  ,A.PLANEJUN
  ,A.REALUN
  ,A.EFFECTIVE_CALLS	
  ,A.UNDER_CALLS	
  ,A.OVER_CALLS	
  ,A.OFF_TARGET_CALLS
  ,A.TARGET_CUST
  ,A.UNDER_TARGET
  ,A.ON_TARGET
  ,A.OVER_TARGET
  ,A.EMAIL_CONSENT_KPI
  ,CASE WHEN A.VRT = A.VP THEN 'S' ELSE'N'END AS AT_DESIRED_FREQUENCY
  ,CASE WHEN A.VRT > A.VP THEN 'S' ELSE'N'END AS OVER_DESIRED_FREQUENCY
  ,'VM'										as TIPO_INTERACAO
FROM
	View_Fato_Visita_Medico A 
WHERE
    EXISTS (SELECT B.* FROM "GSK_Intelligence".dbo."DIM_CAD_FORCA_VENDAS" B WHERE A.CICLO = B.CICLO AND A.ROW_ID_TERRITORIO = B.ROW_ID_TERRITORIO 
            AND B.FLAG_BI IS NULL);

SELECT    
	LEFT(A.DATA,6) AS CICLO
	,A.ID_ENVIO AS ID_ENVIO_EMAIL
	,A.ID_ATIVIDADE AS ID_ATIV_EMAIL
	,A.TIPO_EVENTO AS TIPO_ATIV_EMAIL
	,A.DATA AS DATA_ATIV_EMAIL
	,B.PRODUCT_NAME AS PRODUTO
    ,A.ROW_ID_CONTATO
    ,A.ROW_ID_TERRITORIO
    ,A.NOME_DOCUMENTO_APROVADO AS DOCUMENTO_EMAIL
    ,A.DESCRICAO_DOCUMENTO AS DESC_DOCUMENTO_EMAIL
    ,A.ASSUNTO_EMAIL
	,'E-Mail 1:1'										as TIPO_INTERACAO
FROM
	[GSK_Intelligence].[dbo].[Fato_Email_1_1] A LEFT OUTER JOIN [GSK_Intelligence].[dbo].[STG_Cad_Promo_Items_Veeva] B
    ON	A.ROW_ID_PRODUTO = B.PRODUCT_CATALOG_ID
WHERE 
	LEFT(CAST(LEFT(A.DATA,6)  AS VARCHAR(10)),4) IN (YEAR(GETDATE()),YEAR(GETDATE())-1) AND
    EXISTS (SELECT B.* FROM [GSK_Intelligence].[dbo].[DIM_CAD_FORCA_VENDAS] B WHERE LEFT(A.DATA,6)  = B.CICLO AND A.ROW_ID_TERRITORIO = B.ROW_ID_TERRITORIO AND B.FLAG_BI IS NULL);

SELECT    
	A.ROW_ID_CONTATO,	
    A.ROW_ID_TERRITORIO,
    A.CICLO,	
    A.PRODUTO AS PRODUTO_FRANCHISE,	
    A.FRANCHISE,		
    A.SUB_CATEGORY AS SUB_CAT_FRANCHISE,
    E.PESO AS PESO_FRANCHISE,
	'VF'										as TIPO_INTERACAO
FROM
	"GSK_Intelligence".dbo."Fato_Visitas_Realizadas_Franchise" A 
    LEFT OUTER JOIN (	SELECT 
                          A.CICLO,
                          A.ROW_ID_TERRITORIO,
                          B.PESO,
                          CASE
                          WHEN RIGHT(TERRITORIO,6) = '022010' THEN 'MSL LUPUS'
                          WHEN RIGHT(TERRITORIO,6) = '037000' THEN 'MSL HEALTHECO'
                          WHEN RIGHT(TERRITORIO,6) = '022001' THEN 'MSL VIIV'
                          WHEN RIGHT(TERRITORIO,6) = '022011' THEN 'MSL VIIV'
                          WHEN RIGHT(TERRITORIO,6) = '022012' THEN 'MSL VIIV'
                          WHEN RIGHT(TERRITORIO,6) = '022007' THEN 'MSL RESP'
                          WHEN RIGHT(TERRITORIO,6) = '022009' THEN 'MSL RESP'
                          WHEN RIGHT(TERRITORIO,6) = '036000' THEN 'MSL DPOC'
                          WHEN RIGHT(TERRITORIO,6) = '055001' THEN 'MSL VACINAS'
                          WHEN RIGHT(TERRITORIO,6) = '055002' THEN 'MSL VACINAS'
                          WHEN RIGHT(TERRITORIO,6) = '055003' THEN 'MSL VACINAS'
                          WHEN RIGHT(TERRITORIO,6) = '055004' THEN 'MSL VACINAS'
                          WHEN RIGHT(TERRITORIO,6) = '055005' THEN 'MSL VACINAS'
                          WHEN RIGHT(TERRITORIO,6) = '055006' THEN 'MSL VACINAS'
                          ELSE A.DIVISÃO END AS DIVISAO,
                          B.PRODUTO
                          FROM
							  "GSK_Intelligence".dbo."DIM_CAD_FORCA_VENDAS" A LEFT OUTER JOIN (SELECT * FROM "GSK_Intelligence".dbo."Dim_Cad_FTE_Peso_Produto" WHERE PESO <> '0') B
							  ON  CASE
									  WHEN RIGHT(TERRITORIO,6) = '022010' THEN 'MSL LUPUS'
									  WHEN RIGHT(TERRITORIO,6) = '037000' THEN 'MSL HEALTHECO'
									  WHEN RIGHT(TERRITORIO,6) = '022001' THEN 'MSL VIIV'
									  WHEN RIGHT(TERRITORIO,6) = '022011' THEN 'MSL VIIV'
									  WHEN RIGHT(TERRITORIO,6) = '022012' THEN 'MSL VIIV'
									  WHEN RIGHT(TERRITORIO,6) = '022007' THEN 'MSL RESP'
									  WHEN RIGHT(TERRITORIO,6) = '022009' THEN 'MSL RESP'
									  WHEN RIGHT(TERRITORIO,6) = '036000' THEN 'MSL DPOC'
									  WHEN RIGHT(TERRITORIO,6) = '055001' THEN 'MSL VACINAS'
									  WHEN RIGHT(TERRITORIO,6) = '055002' THEN 'MSL VACINAS'
									  WHEN RIGHT(TERRITORIO,6) = '055003' THEN 'MSL VACINAS'
									  WHEN RIGHT(TERRITORIO,6) = '055004' THEN 'MSL VACINAS'
									  WHEN RIGHT(TERRITORIO,6) = '055005' THEN 'MSL VACINAS'
									  WHEN RIGHT(TERRITORIO,6) = '055006' THEN 'MSL VACINAS'
									  ELSE A.DIVISÃO END = B.DIVISAO

                          WHERE
                          LEFT(CAST(A.CICLO AS VARCHAR(10)),4) IN (YEAR(GETDATE()),YEAR(GETDATE())-1) AND
                          EXISTS (SELECT C.* FROM DIM_CAD_FORCA_VENDAS C WHERE A.CICLO  = C.CICLO AND A.ROW_ID_TERRITORIO = C.ROW_ID_TERRITORIO 
                           
                          AND C.FLAG_BI IS NULL)) E
    ON	A.CICLO = E.CICLO AND
		A.ROW_ID_TERRITORIO = E.ROW_ID_TERRITORIO AND
		A.PRODUTO = E.PRODUTO;

Select
	 A.CICLO + A.CRM AS CRM_CICLO
	,RIGHT(A.CICLO,2) AS MÊS	  
	,A.CICLO
    ,A.CRM
    ,A.MEDICO
    ,A.TIPO
    ,A.TIPOCONTATO
    ,A.GRUPOPROMOCIONAL
    ,A.ESPECIALIDADE
    ,A.LOGRADOURO
    ,A.COMPLEMENTO
    ,A.BAIRRO
    ,A.CIDADE
    ,A.UF
    ,A.CEP
    ,A.BRICK
    ,A.TELEFONEMEDICO
    ,A.CELULARMEDICO
    ,A.EMAIL AS EMAIL_1_1
    ,A.ROW_ID_FUNCIONARIO
    ,A.ROW_ID_TERRITORIO
    ,A.ROW_ID_CONTATO
    ,A.STATUS
    ,A.QTD_VISITA_PLANEJADA AS QTD_VISITA_PLANEJADA_PAINEL
	,A.QTD_VISITA_REALIZADA AS QTD_VISITA_REALIZADA_PAINEL
    ,A.ESPECIALIDADE_02
    ,A.ESPECIALIDADE_03
    ,A.VP_PROX
    ,A.STATUS_MEDICO
    ,A.EMAIL_CONSENT AS EMAIL_1_1_CONSENT
    ,B.NETWORK_ID
    ,B.RX_GIGYA_ID
    ,D.VEEVA_ID
    ,B.ROW_ID_CONTATO_EXT
    ,A.OUTRO_EMAIL AS EMAIL_MASS
    ,A.OUTRO_EMAIL_CONSENT  AS EMAIL_MASS_CONSENT  
    ,CASE 
		WHEN C.CYCLE_PLAN = 'S' THEN 'S'
	 ELSE 'N' END 															AS CYCLE_PLAN,
	 GP.MERCADO,
	 GP.GRUPOPROMOCIONAL as 'PRODUTO_PAINEL'
FROM
	"GSK_Intelligence".dbo."DIM_PAINEL_CORRENTE" A LEFT OUTER JOIN "GSK_Intelligence".dbo."STG_CAD_CONTAS_VEEVA" B
    ON	A.ROW_ID_CONTATO = B.ROW_ID_CONTATO

	Left join "GSK_Intelligence".dbo.Dim_Cad_Grade_Promocional_Aberta_Qlikview as GP
	on A.CRM = GP.CRM AND A.ROW_ID_TERRITORIO = GP.ROW_ID_TERRITORIO
    
    LEFT JOIN "GSK_Intelligence".dbo."Dim_Sense_Universo_Medico" D
      ON D.CRM = B.DOCUMENTO
	  AND D.NETWORK_ID = B.NETWORK_ID
    
    LEFT OUTER JOIN "GSK_Intelligence".dbo."View_Sense_Cycle_Plan" C
	ON	A.CICLO = C.CICLO AND
		A.ROW_ID_CONTATO = C.ROW_ID_CONTATO AND
		A.ROW_ID_TERRITORIO = C.ROW_ID_TERRITORIO
    
WHERE
	LEFT(CAST(A.CICLO AS VARCHAR(10)),4) IN (YEAR(GETDATE()),YEAR(GETDATE())-1) AND
    EXISTS (SELECT B.* FROM "GSK_Intelligence".dbo."DIM_CAD_FORCA_VENDAS" B WHERE A.CICLO = B.CICLO AND A.ROW_ID_TERRITORIO = B.ROW_ID_TERRITORIO 
            AND B.FLAG_BI IS NULL);

SELECT    
	A.BU,
    CASE 
    	WHEN RIGHT(A.TERRITORIO,6) ='022010' THEN 'MSL LUPUS'
        WHEN RIGHT(A.TERRITORIO,6) ='037000' THEN 'MSL HEALTHECO'
        WHEN RIGHT(A.TERRITORIO,6) ='022001' THEN 'MSL VIIV'
        WHEN RIGHT(A.TERRITORIO,6) ='022011' THEN 'MSL VIIV'
        WHEN RIGHT(A.TERRITORIO,6) ='022012' THEN 'MSL VIIV'
        WHEN RIGHT(A.TERRITORIO,6) ='022007' THEN 'MSL RESP'
        WHEN RIGHT(A.TERRITORIO,6) ='022009' THEN 'MSL RESP'
        WHEN RIGHT(A.TERRITORIO,6) ='036000' THEN 'MSL DPOC'
        WHEN RIGHT(A.TERRITORIO,6) ='055001' THEN 'MSL VACINAS'
        WHEN RIGHT(A.TERRITORIO,6) ='055002' THEN 'MSL VACINAS'
        WHEN RIGHT(A.TERRITORIO,6) ='055003' THEN 'MSL VACINAS'
        WHEN RIGHT(A.TERRITORIO,6) ='055004' THEN 'MSL VACINAS'
        WHEN RIGHT(A.TERRITORIO,6) ='055005' THEN 'MSL VACINAS'
        WHEN RIGHT(A.TERRITORIO,6) ='055006' THEN 'MSL VACINAS'
	ELSE A.DIVISÃO END AS DIVISÃO,
    A.NOME_GD,
    A.NOME_GR,
    A.NOME_REPRESENTANTE,
    A.ROW_ID_FUNCIONARIO AS MUDID,
	A.ROW_ID_TERRITORIO,
    A.TERRITORIO,
    A.TERRITORIO_GD,
    A.TERRITORIO_GR,
    A.CICLO AS CICLO_FV,
    A.ROW_ID_FUNCIONARIO,
    A.FLAG_PROJETO,
	CASE WHEN B.ROW_ID_TERRITORIO IS NULL THEN 'N' ELSE 'S' END AS FLAG_TARGET
FROM 
	(SELECT * FROM GSK_Intelligence.dbo.Dim_Cad_Forca_Vendas WHERE FLAG_BI IS NULL) A LEFT OUTER JOIN GSK_Intelligence.dbo.Dim_Rep_Target B
    ON	A.CICLO = B.CICLO AND A.ROW_ID_TERRITORIO = B.ROW_ID_TERRITORIO

	LEFT OUTER JOIN (	SELECT DISTINCT 
							RIGHT(A.CYCLE_PLAN_NAME,6) AS CICLO,
							B.TERRITORY_ID 
						FROM 
							STG_Cad_MCCP_Veeva A LEFT OUTER JOIN STG_CAD_HIERARQUIA_VEEVA B
							ON A.TERRITORY = B.TERRITORIO
						WHERE
							LEFT(RIGHT(CYCLE_PLAN_NAME,6),4) IN (CAST(YEAR(GETDATE()) AS VARCHAR(6)),CAST(YEAR(GETDATE())-1 AS VARCHAR(6)))) C
	ON A.CICLO = C.CICLO AND A.ROW_ID_TERRITORIO = C.TERRITORY_ID
WHERE 
	LEFT(CAST(A.CICLO AS VARCHAR(10)),4) IN (YEAR(GETDATE()),YEAR(GETDATE())-1) AND
    EXISTS (SELECT B.* FROM GSK_Intelligence.dbo.DIM_CAD_FORCA_VENDAS B WHERE A.CICLO = B.CICLO AND A.ROW_ID_TERRITORIO = B.ROW_ID_TERRITORIO 
            AND B.FLAG_BI IS NULL);

SELECT    
   CICLO
  ,DIVISAO	
  ,TARGET_CRM	AS TARGET_SRO_CRM
  ,TARGET_VISITA	AS TARGET_SRO_VISITA
  ,TARGET_MEDIA_DIA	 AS TARGET_SRO_MEDIA_DIA
  ,TARGET_COACHING	AS TARGET_SRO_COACHING
  ,TARGET_COBERTURA AS TARGET_SRO_COB
FROM
	"GSK_Intelligence".dbo."Dim_Cad_Target_SRO";

Select distinct  
	CASE 
		WHEN RIGHT(A.CICLO,2) = '12' THEN CAST((CAST(LEFT(A.CICLO,4) AS INT)+1) AS VARCHAR(4))+'01'
	ELSE A.CICLO+1 END AS CICLO_QUAD,
	A.CRM AS CRM_QUAD,
    A.MERCADO AS MERCADO_QUAD,
    A.CATEGORIA AS CATEGORIA_QUAD,
    A.MKT_SHARE_MEDICO AS MKT_SHARE_QUAD,
    A.CLASSIFICACAO AS QUADRANTE_QUAD,
    A.JORNADA AS JORNADA_QUAD
From
	"GSK_Intelligence".dbo."Dim_Quadrante_Medico" A
Where 
	LEFT(CAST(A.CICLO AS VARCHAR(10)),4) IN (YEAR(GETDATE()),YEAR(GETDATE())-1) AND
    EXISTS (SELECT B.* FROM "GSK_Intelligence".dbo."DIM_AUDIT_END" B WHERE A.CRM = B.CRM);
